lead_paragraph: Kyle Lowry scored 10 of his 25 points in the fourth quarter and DeMar DeRozan added 19 to lead the Toronto Raptors to a 108-95 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Lowry, DeRozan Lead Raptors to 108-95 Win Over 76ers
